---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <p>
    The Muslim American Society of Minnesota ("MAS MN") collects two categories of information
    through this website: personal information you provide directly, such as your zip code or
    email address, and aggregated usage data. IP addresses are logged for system administration
    purposes only, remain anonymous, and are not linked to personally identifiable information.
  </p>
  <h2>How we use information</h2>
  <p>
    Information collected is used to improve site content and personalize your experience. We
    will never disclose your personally identifiable information to a third party unless
    required to do so by court order, law, or governmental agency.
  </p>
  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    This site may use cookies containing a randomly assigned user ID to streamline login and
    site functionality. You can configure your browser to decline cookies if you prefer.
  </p>
  <h2>Third parties</h2>
  <p>
    Third-party vendors may place advertising cookies on this site. These parties maintain their
    own privacy policies and may participate in the Network Advertising Initiative (NAI), which
    offers a consumer opt-out mechanism.
  </p>
  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time, with at least 30 days'
    notice before changes take effect.
  </p>
  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>
    Direct any privacy questions to <a href="mailto:info@masmn.org">info@masmn.org</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
